{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01A5SpARSbfY1Ky8nXfMLwv6","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t----------------------------- MODULE VoteProof_VInv1 ------------------------------\n2\t\n3\tEXTENDS Integers , FiniteSets, TLC, TLAPS\n4\t\n5\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n6\tCONSTANT Value,     \n7\t         Acceptor,  \n8\t         Quorum     \n9\t\n10\tASSUME QA == /\\ \\A Q \\in Quorum : Q \\subseteq Acceptor\n11\t             /\\ \\A Q1, Q2 \\in Quorum : Q1 \\cap Q2 # {}  \n12\t \n13\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n14\t\n15\tBallot == Nat\n16\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n17\t\n18\tVARIABLES votes, maxBal\n19\t\n20\tVotedFor(a, b, v) == <<b, v>> \\in votes[a]\n21\t\n22\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n23\t\n24\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n25\t\n26\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n27\t\n28\tAXIOM SimpleNatInduction == \\A f : /\\ f[0]\n29\t                                   /\\ \\A n \\in Nat : f[n] => f[n+1]\n30\t                                   => \\A n \\in Nat : f[n]\n31\t\n32\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n33\t\n34\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n35\t\n36\tVInv1 == \\A a \\in Acceptor, b \\in Ballot, v, w \\in Value : \n37\t           VotedFor(a, b, v) /\\ VotedFor(a, b, w) => (v = w)\n38\t\n39\tVInv3 ==  \\A a1, a2 \\in Acceptor, b \\in Ballot, v1, v2 \\in Value : \n40\t                VotedFor(a1, b, v1) /\\ VotedFor(a2, b, v2) => (v1 = v2)\n41\t\n42\tTHEOREM VInv3 => VInv1\n43\tPROOF OBVIOUS\n44\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n45\t\n46\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n47\t\n48\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n49\t\n50\tASSUME AcceptorNonempty == Acceptor # {}\n51\t\n52\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n53\t\n54\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n55\t\n56\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n57\t\n58\tASSUME AcceptorFinite == IsFiniteSet(Acceptor)\n59\t\n60\tASSUME ValueNonempty == Value # {}\n61\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n62\t\n63\tAXIOM SubsetOfFiniteSetFinite == \n64\t        \\A S, T : IsFiniteSet(T) /\\ (S \\subseteq T) => IsFiniteSet(S)\n65\t\n66\tAXIOM FiniteSetHasMax == \n67\t        \\A S \\in SUBSET Int :\n68\t          IsFiniteSet(S) /\\ (S # {}) => \\E max \\in S : \\A x \\in S : max >= x\n69\t\n70\tAXIOM IntervalFinite == \\A i, j \\in Int : IsFiniteSet(i..j)\n71\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n72\t\n73\t-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n74\t\n75\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n76\t\n77\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n78\t\n79\t===============================================================================\n80\t\n81\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5472e5c8-8cce-4b25-869e-83fc35245f7c","uuid":"cc4f6bdf-388f-4ada-b048-aadca12b8b64","timestamp":"2026-05-27T08:45:26.879Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/tmp/claude_code_bench_VoteProof_VInv1_xzilkoie/VoteProof_VInv1.tla","content":"----------------------------- MODULE VoteProof_VInv1 ------------------------------\n\nEXTENDS Integers , FiniteSets, TLC, TLAPS\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\nCONSTANT Value,     \n         Acceptor,  \n         Quorum     \n\nASSUME QA == /\\ \\A Q \\in Quorum : Q \\subseteq Acceptor\n             /\\ \\A Q1, Q2 \\in Quorum : Q1 \\cap Q2 # {}  \n \n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nBallot == Nat\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nVARIABLES votes, maxBal\n\nVotedFor(a, b, v) == <<b, v>> \\in votes[a]\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nAXIOM SimpleNatInduction == \\A f : /\\ f[0]\n                                   /\\ \\A n \\in Nat : f[n] => f[n+1]\n                                   => \\A n \\in Nat : f[n]\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nVInv1 == \\A a \\in Acceptor, b \\in Ballot, v, w \\in Value : \n           VotedFor(a, b, v) /\\ VotedFor(a, b, w) => (v = w)\n\nVInv3 ==  \\A a1, a2 \\in Acceptor, b \\in Ballot, v1, v2 \\in Value : \n                VotedFor(a1, b, v1) /\\ VotedFor(a2, b, v2) => (v1 = v2)\n\nTHEOREM VInv3 => VInv1\nPROOF OBVIOUS\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nASSUME AcceptorNonempty == Acceptor # {}\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nASSUME AcceptorFinite == IsFiniteSet(Acceptor)\n\nASSUME ValueNonempty == Value # {}\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nAXIOM SubsetO